---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="American Idolatry — The Babylon We Were Born Into | Nazaryah"
  description="Ten connected studies walking through the pagan architecture, symbols, holidays, and oaths of American civic religion — and the call to come out of her."
>
  <div class="ai-wrap">

    <!-- Decorative star field -->
    <div class="ai-star-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-large" style="top: 5%; left: 8%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-red" style="top: 12%; right: 12%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-tiny" style="top: 22%; left: 25%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star" style="top: 30%; right: 30%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-large ai-star-red" style="top: 45%; left: 5%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-tiny" style="top: 52%; right: 18%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star" style="top: 60%; left: 40%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-red" style="top: 68%; right: 5%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-large" style="top: 78%; left: 15%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-tiny" style="top: 85%; right: 35%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star" style="top: 92%; left: 50%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-red ai-star-large" style="top: 35%; left: 60%;">★</span>
      <span class="ai-star ai-star-tiny" style="top: 18%; left: 70%;">★</span>
    </div>

    <main class="ai-main">

      <!-- BANNER -->
      <header class="ai-banner">
        <h1 class="ai-banner-title">American Idolatry</h1>
        <p class="ai-banner-sub">The Babylon We Were Born Into</p>
        <div class="ai-banner-stripes">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- INTRO -->
      <section class="ai-intro">
        <p>Most American believers think of Babylon as something far away — ancient, foreign, somewhere in the desert. It is not. Babylon is the system of empire-religion that began at Babel and has been passed down, capital by capital, through every modern nation that carries her symbols forward.</p>
        <p>Her signatures are obelisks, eternal flames, eagle standards, deified rulers, all-seeing eyes, and harvest festivals to the Queen of Heaven. They are stamped on the National Mall, the dollar bill, the Pledge of Allegiance, and the calendar of every national holiday.</p>
        <div class="ai-scripture">
          "Come out of her, my people, that ye be not partakers of her sins."<br>
          <span class="ai-scripture-ref">— Revelation 18:4</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CORNERSTONE -->
      <section class="ai-cornerstone">
        <div class="ai-cornerstone-stars" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="s" style="top: 8%; left: 5%; font-size: 18px;">★</span>
          <span class="s" style="top: 20%; right: 8%; font-size: 24px;">★</span>
          <span class="s" style="top: 50%; left: 92%; font-size: 14px;">★</span>
          <span class="s" style="bottom: 15%; left: 8%; font-size: 20px;">★</span>
          <span class="s" style="bottom: 25%; right: 15%; font-size: 16px;">★</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-cornerstone-label">Start Here · The Cornerstone</div>
        <h2 class="ai-cornerstone-title">The Faith of the Founders</h2>
        <p class="ai-cornerstone-poetic">What They Actually Believed</p>
        <p class="ai-cornerstone-pitch">Before any other study in this section will land, the reader has to face <em>who actually built America</em>. Their own pastors, their own letters, and their own ratified treaties tell the story modern Christianity has been hiding for two centuries. Thomas Paine called the Bible the word of a demon. George Washington's pastor of twenty years admitted he had never confessed Christ. The Senate of 1797 declared, in writing, that the United States is not in any sense founded on the Christian religion. <em>This is the foundation everything else rests on.</em></p>
        <a href="/american-idolatry/faith-of-the-founders" class="ai-cornerstone-btn">★ Read the Cornerstone ★</a>
      </section>

      <!-- DIVIDER -->
      <div class="ai-section-divider">
        <span>The Nine Supporting Studies</span>
        <span class="ai-star-cluster">★ ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ ★</span>
      </div>

      <!-- STUDY GRID -->
      <div class="ai-study-grid">

        <a href="/american-idolatry/patriotism" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY ONE ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">Patriotism</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Idolatry We Don't Name</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/july-4" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY TWO ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">July 4th</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Blazing Star Over America</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/washington-dc" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY THREE ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">Washington DC</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Sun Temple on the Potomac</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/memorial-veterans-day" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY FOUR ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">Memorial &amp; Veterans Day</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Cult of the Fallen Soldier</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/thanksgiving" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY FIVE ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">Thanksgiving</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Harvest Festival in Pilgrim Costume</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/pledge-of-allegiance" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY SIX ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">The Pledge of Allegiance</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">An Idol Oath in Thirty-One Words</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/dollar-bill" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY SEVEN ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">The Dollar Bill</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">The Great Seal and the Hidden Eye</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/presidents" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY EIGHT ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">The Presidents</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">Apotheosis of the American Caesars</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/american-idolatry/national-cathedral" class="ai-study-card">
          <div class="ai-number">★ STUDY NINE ★</div>
          <div class="ai-direct-title">The National Cathedral</div>
          <div class="ai-poetic-title">Empire in Church Clothes</div>
          <div class="ai-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>

      <!-- FOOTER CALL -->
      <div class="ai-footer-call">
        <p class="ai-verse">"Come out of her, my people, that ye be not partakers of her sins, and that ye receive not of her plagues."</p>
        <p class="ai-ref">★ Revelation 18:4 ★</p>
        <div class="ai-footer-stripes">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ai-wrap {
    --navy: #0a1d3a;
    --navy-deep: #061230;
    --red: #b8232a;
    --red-deep: #8a1a20;
    --cream: #f5f1e6;
    --parchment: #ebe3cf;
    --gold: #c9a961;
    --ink: #1a1a1a;
    --ink-soft: #3a3a3a;

    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* STAR FIELD */
  .ai-star-field {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ai-star {
    position: absolute;
    color: var(--navy);
    opacity: 0.06;
    font-size: 22px;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .ai-star.ai-star-red { color: var(--red); opacity: 0.05; }
  .ai-star.ai-star-large { font-size: 38px; opacity: 0.04; }
  .ai-star.ai-star-tiny { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.08; }

  .ai-main {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 32px 120px;
  }

  /* BANNER */
  .ai-banner {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px 60px;
    border-top: 8px solid var(--red);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--navy);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(10,29,58,0.03) 100%);
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-banner::before, .ai-banner::after {
    content: '★';
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 28px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
  }
  .ai-banner::before { left: 40px; }
  .ai-banner::after { right: 40px; }

  .ai-banner-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--navy-deep);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }
  .ai-banner-sub {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
    color: var(--red-deep);
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }
  .ai-banner-stripes {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .ai-banner-stripes span {
    display: block;
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
  }
  .ai-banner-stripes span:nth-child(odd) { background: var(--red); }
  .ai-banner-stripes span:nth-child(even) { background: var(--navy); }

  /* INTRO */
  .ai-intro {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 60px auto;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .ai-intro p { margin: 0 0 18px 0; }
  .ai-scripture {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--navy);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--navy);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--navy);
    padding: 18px 0;
    margin: 30px auto;
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .ai-scripture-ref {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--red-deep);
  }

  /* CORNERSTONE */
  .ai-cornerstone {
    margin: 80px 0 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-deep) 0%, var(--navy) 100%);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 60px 50px;
    position: relative;
    border-left: 12px solid var(--red);
    border-right: 12px solid var(--red);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 80%, rgba(184,35,42,0.18) 0%, transparent 35%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-stars {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-stars .s {
    position: absolute;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.25;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-label {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-label::before {
    content: '★ ';
    color: var(--red);
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-label::after {
    content: ' ★';
    color: var(--red);
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-poetic {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 0 30px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-pitch {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(245,241,230,0.9);
    margin: 0 0 36px 0;
    max-width: 720px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-pitch em {
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 18px 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border: 3px solid var(--cream);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-cornerstone-btn:hover {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--red-deep);
  }

  /* SECTION DIVIDER */
  .ai-section-divider {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 80px 0 50px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ai-section-divider > span:first-child {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  .ai-section-divider > span:first-child::before,
  .ai-section-divider > span:first-child::after {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--navy);
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin: 0 20px;
  }
  .ai-star-cluster {
    display: block;
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-top: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
  }

  /* STUDY GRID */
  .ai-study-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(310px, 1fr));
    gap: 28px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .ai-study-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 2px solid var(--navy);
    padding: 36px 28px 32px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ai-study-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--red);
  }
  .ai-study-card::after {
    content: '★';
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px;
    right: 16px;
    color: var(--navy);
    opacity: 0.15;
    font-size: 28px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }
  .ai-study-card:hover {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(10,29,58,0.25);
  }
  .ai-study-card:hover::after {
    color: var(--red);
    opacity: 1;
    transform: rotate(15deg);
  }
  .ai-study-card:hover .ai-direct-title { color: var(--cream); }
  .ai-study-card:hover .ai-poetic-title { color: var(--gold); }
  .ai-study-card:hover .ai-arrow { color: var(--gold); }

  .ai-number {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .ai-direct-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--navy-deep);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .ai-poetic-title {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .ai-arrow {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
  }

  /* FOOTER CALL */
  .ai-footer-call {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 100px;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    border-top: 4px double var(--navy);
    border-bottom: 4px double var(--navy);
    background: var(--parchment);
  }
  .ai-verse {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--navy-deep);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .ai-ref {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--red-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .ai-footer-stripes {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }
  .ai-footer-stripes span {
    display: block;
    width: 30px;
    height: 3px;
  }
  .ai-footer-stripes span:nth-child(odd) { background: var(--red); }
  .ai-footer-stripes span:nth-child(even) { background: var(--navy); }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .ai-main { padding: 30px 16px 80px; }
    .ai-banner { padding: 30px 12px 40px; }
    .ai-banner::before, .ai-banner::after { display: none; }
    .ai-cornerstone { padding: 40px 24px; border-left-width: 8px; border-right-width: 8px; }
    .ai-study-card { padding: 30px 22px 26px; }
  }
</style>
